Hello, All;
Apparently there is a system / filtering error. I have been working on getting everyone's information squared away in preparation for ordering the various perks like the t-shirts.  There was literally one disputed charge (I know it's not you) and for some reason that message, though filtered to just that individual seems to have gone to everyone. Ahhh!!! 
Regardless, if you've filled out your survey thank you. If you've still not done done so, please do. Several people have pointed out that the survey hit their spam filter for some reason (please check there).
